, and role awareness.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 4aGenderfrage. 4aGeschlechterkonflikt. 4aHeroides. 4aMetamorphose. 4aOvid-Rezeption. 4aSexualisierte Gewalt.  aHeroides.  aMetamorphoses.  agender issues.  areception of Ovid.  asexualised violence.1 aEickmeyer, Jost, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aEming, Jutta, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHolzberg, Niklas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKasper, Judith, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMöller, Melanie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMöller, Melanie, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aPauly, Yvonne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVinken, Barbara, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aZepp, Susanne, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Ebook Package 2020z978311069627108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2020z9783110704518oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Classical Studies 2020z9783110704631oZDB-23-DGD0 cEPUBz97831107032690 cprintz978311070296540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311070322140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110703221423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110703221.jpg  a978-3-11-069627-1  DG Ebook Package 2020b2020  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGDb2020  aZDB-23-DGGb2020